# 🚀 AI-Assistant – AI-Powered Calendar Assistant

AI-Assistant is an intelligent assistant built using **Next.js**, **OpenRouter LLM**, and **Google Calendar integration via OAuth**.  
It can talk like ChatGPT, and also fetch your calendar events (for today, tomorrow, or any date) automatically.

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Google OAuth 2.0 login
- ✅ Secure access to your calendar events
- ✅ Natural language prompts like:
  - "What’s on my calendar today?"
  - "Do I have anything scheduled tomorrow?"
  - "Any meetings on 28th July?"
- ✅ Chat-based interface with AI responses

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

- **Next.js** (App Router)
- **OpenRouter LLM (GPT-3.5/4)** – for assistant intelligence
- **Google OAuth + Calendar API** – for 3rd party integration
- **Vercel AI SDK** – for chat streaming
- **NextAuth.js** – for authentication
- **chrono-node** – for parsing natural date queries

---

